               <p>RICHARD SOUTHEE. I live in <placeName id="t18270215-46-crimeloc250">Mark-lane</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18270215-46-crimeloc250" type="placeName" value="Mark-lane"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18270215-46-crimeloc250" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18270215-46-off248 t18270215-46-crimeloc250"></join>. On Friday last, this great coat was in my surgery; I saw the prisoner leave my door with it under his arm - I followed, and overtook him within six yards - I saw him drop it; two other persons were about; I had had it five or six weeks - I think the lowest value of it is 3l. - I have lost three within the last year.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18270215-46-person356">
                  JOHN 
                  COCKBURN
               <interp inst="t18270215-46-person356" type="surname" value="COCKBURN"></interp>
