                     <interp inst="t18270215-46-person356" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am servant to Mr. Southee. I hung this coat in the surgery, not ten minutes before it was taken; I saw the prisoner go out with it; I went out, and saw him drop it.</p>
